import React from 'react'
import { Input, Form, Label } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const TemperatureInput = () => (
    <Form>
        <Label>Temperatura</Label>
        <Input fluid
        label={{ basic: true, content: '°C' }}
        labelPosition='right'
        placeholder='Graus...'
    />
    </Form>
)

export default TemperatureInput
